data.description: Make an appointment to see this charming rambler in the White City community.  The main floor has new carpet.  (there is hardwood covering the entire main floor under the carpet - if you look in the closets you can see what they look like).  Brand new electrical panel and roof.  The fully fenced backyard is huge and perfect for entertaining or a great game of soccer.  There is a large shed included in the sale perfect for storing all of your extra toys.    Please do not show without appointment and make sure all doors are locked before you exit. All information including square footage has been provided as a courtesy.   Buyer and buyers agent to verify all information.
